</head>

<body lang=EN-US style='tab-interval:.5in;word-wrap:break-word'>

<div class=WordSection1>

<h1><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>FieldPass
<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>Club Manager Guide<o:p></o:p></span></h1>

<p class=muted><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>For
Club Managers: login, update club branding, and submit lineup before match day.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<div style='border:solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #DDDDDD .75pt;
padding:10.0pt 10.0pt 10.0pt 10.0pt'>

<p class=req style='background:#FAFAFA'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext'>Important
rule (Lineup deadline):</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='background:#FAFAFA'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext'>You should submit your player lineup <b>at
least 24 hours before</b> the real match kickoff time. If you wait too late,
the system/admin may lock the lineup and you may not be able to submit.</span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

</div>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>1)
Login (Club Manager)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p class=muted><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Club
managers use the <b>admin portal</b> with <b>Malaysia (+60) mobile OTP</b> â€”
the same flow as association admins (not username/password).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Open
     the admin login page in your browser (example: <b>http://localhost:8000/admin/login</b>).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Enter
     your <b>mobile number</b> (national digits only, after +60 â€” no spaces).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Click
     <b>Send OTP</b>. You will receive a one-time code (SMS/WhatsApp, depending
     on integration).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Enter
     the <b>OTP code</b>, optionally tick <b>Remember me</b>, then click <b>Verify
     &amp; Sign In</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

<p class=muted><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>The
phone number must match the one stored on your admin account. If login fails,
ask your association admin to confirm your number under <b>Admins â†’ Edit</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>2)
Update Club Logo<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>From
     the left sidebar, go to <b>Clubs</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Find
     your club and click <b>Edit</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>In
     the <b>Avatar / Logo</b> section: <o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <ul type=circle>
  <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
      auto;mso-list:l7 level2 lfo2;tab-stops:list 1.0in'><span
      style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
      "Times New Roman"'>Click <b>Choose File</b> and select a PNG/JPG image.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
  <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
      auto;mso-list:l7 level2 lfo2;tab-stops:list 1.0in'><span
      style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
      "Times New Roman"'>Keep it square if possible (recommended for clean
      display in tables and headers).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 </ul>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Click
     <b>Save / Update</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3)
Update Club Jersey (Home/Away)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p class=muted><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>If
your system shows jersey uploads (or â€śkitâ€ť images), update them the same
way as the logo.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l5 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Go
     to <b>Clubs</b> â†’ <b>Edit</b> your club.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l5 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Locate
     the <b>Jersey / Kit</b> fields (Home / Away).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l5 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Upload
     images (PNG/JPG) and click <b>Save / Update</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4)
Submit Player Lineup (24 hours before match)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>From
     the sidebar, go to <b>Matches</b> (or <b>Match</b>).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Find
     the upcoming match for your club.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Open
     the match and look for <b>Lineup</b> / <b>Player Lineup</b> / <b>Submit
     Lineup</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list .5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Select
     players for: <o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <ul type=circle>
  <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
      auto;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo4;tab-stops:list 1.0in'><b><span
      style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
      "Times New Roman"'>Starting XI</span></b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
      font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></li>
