     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>If
     itâ€™s within 24 hours of kickoff, the match may be locked.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>C)
